    {
      "instruction": "<p>Bash the <strong>cucumber</strong> with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and chop it into large, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Tip: Bash the cucumber in the bag to avoid mess. By bruising the cucumber, the water is drawn out more easily!</p><p>Combine the <strong>bashed cucumber</strong> and <strong>remaining tamari soy sauce</strong> in a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>bashed cucumber salad</strong></p>",
